Do you want to play a game?

Here's some good ones that are easy to play:
2048, bombardier, phear, gnugo, greed, netris, ninvaders, nsnake, pacman4console, piu-piu, robotfindskitten, sudoku

But the real fun games are for those proficient in the command line...
In order to play the rogue-like games, you need to learn the vim movement keys.

Practice using the game: pacvim
h - left
j - down
k - up
l - right

Rogue-likes:
hunt, nethack, angband, crawl, moria, omega-rpg, slashem
